title: DollHouse
overview: You've seen her dominate South Central Baddies, stir the pot on Deja Vu, and keep it real on Greek Life. Now Joce is taking center stage as the host of the hottest new reality series, where bold personalities and big drama all live under one roof. Expect raw emotions, shocking twists, alliances, betrayals, and unfiltered vibes every episode. This is reality TV like you've never seen before!
